Example to show how to use avro storage in pig.

-- Author Xiaming Chen
-- chenxm35@gmail.com

HOWTO
-----

#cd pig-avro-example
#hadoop fs -put sample-small.avro

If your pig works against hadoop-0.20.x or 1.x, please 
register piggyback as version 20;
If your pig works against hadoop-0.23.x or 2.x, please
register piggyback as version 23;
The run

#pig example.pig
#hfs -tail traffic.stat/part-r-00000
DEST-2F-01	11	9
TSG-1-3F-01	396	353
TSG-2-3F-02	5942	6823
YXL-2-5F-03	1020	988
YXL-3-1F-05	5	4
BYGTSG-4F-06	155	139